{"tid":434191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又一單]波子事件翻版　客踩藥房貓尾被抓傷報警追究","createTime":"2017-10-13T04:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T05:07:43.000Z","uid":70985,"like":9,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"489b9ac1dac977909d746148a28b56118e450e24","tid":434191,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171013/photo/bkn-20171013110304887-1013_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171013123825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171013%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171013110304887-1013_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171013123825&h=d0cd57a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼觀塘藥房貓「波子」被投訴傷人而一度遭漁護署「預約拘捕」，再有藥房貓捲入傷人事件。沙田區一個屋邨的藥房昨日(12日)被顧客投訴，指被其所養的藥房貓抓傷，顧客家人除了報警更揚言要通知漁護署，追究責任。惟藥房職員翻查閉路電視，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現該顧客不慎踩貓尾在先，藥房貓只是出於自衞</span>，職員擔心藥房貓會因此而要坐「動物監」。<br />\n<br />\n該藥房職員透露，昨早該顧客來藥房購物，數小時後折返，聲稱昨早被藥房貓攻擊，他們即場報警，聲言要追究責任，救護車隨後亦到場。該藥房職員指，藥房貓出生至今4年來，一直在藥房看守名貴藥材，捉捕老鼠和蟑螂：「我哋養貓唔係為咗玩，佢喺我哋忠實嘅員工！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171013/photo/bkn-20171013110304887-1013_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171013123825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171013%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171013110304887-1013_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171013123825&h=6437ab2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藥房職員翻查閉路電視，發現該顧客不慎踩貓尾在先，藥房貓只是出於自衞。(趙瑞麟攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171013/photo/bkn-20171013110304887-1013_00822_001_03b.jpg?20171013123825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171013%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171013110304887-1013_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20171013123825&h=e512ce0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田一間藥房被顧客投訴，指被其所養的貓抓傷，並報警求助。(受訪者提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171013/photo/bkn-20171013110304887-1013_00822_001_04b.jpg?20171013123825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171013%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171013110304887-1013_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20171013123825&h=d40af97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有職員擔心藥房貓會因事件而要坐「動物監」。(趙瑞麟攝)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己踩親人條尾先，仲惡人先告狀"},{"pid":"3e21736c8395c4186ec294eceaaaaff40d69fb42","tid":434191,"uid":68094,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2615d683c323d2d4c4ca4a4a5c5d476f4f54b75","tid":434191,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"咁都踩得中<br />\n是故意定不慎？"},{"pid":"3bf828c2093595cd798c0114decdbd4d52f6033d","tid":434191,"uid":37413,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"係咪應該告佢虐畜呢"},{"pid":"35792131a6fd015090ca53a3cffa2100fc089e6f","tid":434191,"uid":39786,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"比大陸人打尖, 行街撞到車, 手拉車碌到你隻腳又唔見你咁惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea591ad77231dc75e6d65904db41c7a3985e498","tid":434191,"uid":61463,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:09:25.000Z","msg":"惡人先告狀死全家!!!"},{"pid":"34b97bab0575fa698862be45f55d91f331e8a5e1","tid":434191,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a15383fb570f7b5735de5f4981be0f415cfcd17","tid":434191,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":77,"score":-75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:10:37.000Z","msg":"做生意就咪養動物啦<br />\n<br />\n9成支那人屈賠錢"},{"pid":"15d8e2268ec03186bf0a4747124dd690d1b1a132","tid":434191,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s